        "reaction_type_english": "Hydrodeoxygenation-Isomerization reaction",
        "description": "在高压釜反应器中，使用Pt/M-SAPO-11和PtSn/M-SAPO-11系列催化剂，对脂肪酸甲酯（FAME）进行一步加氢处理，生产C15-C18烷烃和异构烷烃。",
        "text_snippet": "The catalytic activity of catalyst on the FAME hydrotreatment to produce C15-C18 alkanes was carried out in a high-pressure tank reactor... Pt/Fe3SAPO-11 showed a remarkable catalytic performance containing efficiency of deoxygenation with 100 %, selectivity of C15-C18 alkanes with 99.6 %, and selectivity of iso-C15-C18 alkanes with 34.8 % in one-step hydrotreatment process of fatty acid methyl ester.",
        "reaction_type_classify": "Hydrogenation reaction"
      },
      {
        "experiment_id": 2,
        "reaction_type": "加氢脱氧-异构化反应",
        "reaction_type_english": "Hydrodeoxygenation-Isomerization reaction",
        "description": "在固定床反应器中，使用Pt1Sn1/Fe3SAPO-11催化剂，对FAME进行加氢处理，评估催化剂的长期稳定性。",
        "text_snippet": "The stability was evaluated in a fixed-bed reactor with the inner diameter of 10 mm using catalyst shape of 40–60 meshes... Pt1Sn1/Fe3SAPO-11 with a stable catalytic ability can run as long as 1300 h in a mild reaction condition.",
        "reaction_type_classify": "Hydrogenation reaction"
      }
